value.name: 8/10: Manhunt for James DiMaggio ends in Idaho; Heavy rain triggers mudslides in Colorado
value.description: The hunt for murder-abduction suspect James Lee DiMaggio has ended. DiMaggio reportedly was fatally shot by authorities in Idaho. Hannah Anderson, the kidnapped teenage girl, was found safe ...

value.name: Amber Alert suspect's family wants DNA test on Hannah Anderson, brother
value.description: Andrew Spanswick, a spokesman for the family of James Lee DiMaggio, said rumors have circulated ... in the rubble of DiMaggio's burned home. Police have not confirmed that information.

value.name: Hannah Anderson's mom and brother tortured before death, warrants show
value.description: The warrants also show that Anderson and her suspected captor James Lee DiMaggio exchanged 13 phone calls on the day of the abduction. Norah O'Donnell reports.
